problem with the box, but rather was questioning the interpretation 
of the person using it.  You&#39;re anything but a failure, and my 
inability to hear what he hears is certainly no reflection on you.  
I&#39;ve heard amazing stuff out of your contraptions, so I know it&#39;s 
real and it works.  So much of this is subjective though.  The one 
EVP I consider my most profound success is inaudible to everyone I&#39;ve 
played it for.  Sometimes I feel like I&#39;ll go crazy because it&#39;s so 
absolutely clear to me--How is it possible that no one else can hear 
it??  I also agree that the most success in this field will come from 
good intentions and a pure heart, because this is spiritual work as 
much as it is scientific.  Just wanted to say I appreciate and admire 
you.
